2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes an end-to-end learning approach for video super-resolution. 
3. cs.MM (Multimedia) is another possible category as the paper deals with enhancing the quality of videos. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper proposes a deep learning-based approach for video super-resolution. 
5. cs.GR (Graphics) is also a possible category as the paper deals with image warping and motion compensation, which are techniques commonly used in computer graphics.
